text: Junkee.com is an Australian website that talks about popular culture and news. It is managed by a company called Junkee Media. The website writes about many different topics such as movies, university life, food, TV shows, politics, travel, jobs, health, and things happening on the Internet. It is mainly aimed at people who are between 18 and 29 years old. ==References== Category:Australian websites
title: Junkee
